Join Littlebox x Myfroyoland Summer Splash Giveaway!

You and your two besties now have the chance to WIN the Littlebox Summer Collection and enjoy a treat day at Myfroyoland — because everything’s better with your style squad by your side! 💖

How to Enter:

1. Tag 2 of your besties in the comments and ask them what their favourite summer outfit and dessert is!

2. Make sure all three of you follow these accounts:
@littlebox.india  @myfroyoland @littlebox.club @littlebox.wit (we’re watching!)

3. Share this post to your story for extra brownie points!

Prizes:

Three lucky winners (you and your tagged besties) will receive:

- Littlebox Summer Collection goodies.

- A chill treat day at Myfroyoland (Applicable all over India).

Winner Announcement: 17th May, 2025

Get tagging, spreading the summer vibes, and good luck!
